data.description: The beautiful two-story features a six-bedroom, four-and-a-half-bathroom home in the Indian Trails neighborhood! This spacious and luxurious home offers an array of amenities in a prime location. Step inside and be greeted by a stylishly furnished living area, perfect for relaxing and spending quality time with loved ones. The updated and well-equipped kitchen offers everything you need to prepare full-course dinners. The newly rear-fenced yard of this house is a true oasis designed for entertainment and relaxation. A large paver patio sets the stage for outdoor gatherings, while a playset with a sandbox ensures endless fun for the little ones A hammock invites you to unwind and sway gently in the breeze. Also, a built in firepit and bench offers a cozy ambiance for evening gatherings. The screened lanai with a 6-foot diameter spa with built in seats that waterfalls into the large pool with built in stairs and ledge seating provides a relaxing private escape, allowing you to exercise or unwind. It has abundant amenities, spacious accommodations, and a prime location within 3 minutes from I-95. In addition, many upgrades installed, including a few are a New roof (2020) with upgraded underlayment for hurricane protection, New vinyl flooring in the living room, two bedrooms and hallway (2020-2022), New lighting, New upgraded hurricane-proof encasement windows on the front of the house (2022), New 2 level paver patio with electrical outlets, outdoor lighting and fire pit with bench and walkways, New appliances (2022-2023), Reverse Osmosis Water Treatment System, Installed Smart home thermostat and door lock, New upstairs AC Unit (2022). Please see the attachments for the complete upgrades list. This home is a great investment property already with a management company and set up for Airbnb rentals! It is ultimately set up, furnished, and move-in or rental-ready!
